'''鹽腺'''是[[板鳃亚纲|板鳃亚纲]]、[[海鳥|海鳥]]和一些[[爬行動物|爬行動物]]用來排出[[鹽分|鹽分]]的[[器官|器官]]。其中[[鯊魚|鯊魚]]的鹽腺位于[[直腸|直腸]]，鳥類和爬行動物則位于頭部的[[眼睛|眼睛]]、[[鼻子|鼻子]]或[[嘴|嘴]]附近。其發達程度在不同物種身上不盡相同<ref>{{cite journal|last=Ellis|first=Richard A.|author2=GOERTEMILLER, CLARENCE C. |author3=STETSON, DAVID L |title=Significance of extensive /'leaky/' cell junctions in the avian salt gland|journal=Nature|year=1982|volume=268|pages=555–556|bibcode=1977Natur.268..555E|doi=10.1038/268555a0|pmid=887174|issue=5620}}</ref>。鹽腺的存在使得更有效的[[渗透调节|渗透调节]]成爲可能，因此這些動物才可以直接飲用[[海水|海水]]<ref name=OandE>{{cite web |url=http://www.cartage.org.lb/en/themes/sciences/Zoology/AnimalPhysiology/Osmoregulation/Osmoregulation.htm |title=Osmoregulation and Excretion |accessdate=2007-07-06 |last=O’Driscoll |first=K.J. |author2=Staniels, L.K. |author3=Facey, D.E. |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140205081407/http://www.cartage.org.lb/en/themes/sciences/Zoology/AnimalPhysiology/Osmoregulation/Osmoregulation.htm |archivedate=2014-02-05 }}</ref>。鳥與龜身上存在鹽腺也從另外一個方面説明了它們的[[腎|腎]]功能不如[[哺乳動物|哺乳動物]]完善，畢竟在海生哺乳類動物身上並不存在鹽腺<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ansci.cornell.edu/plants/adapt/salt.html |title=Plants Poisonous to Livestock - Cornell University Department of Animal Science |publisher=Ansci.cornell.edu |accessdate=2011-07-14 |archive-date=2014-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140617030237/https://ansci.cornell.edu/plants/adapt/salt.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而它們皮膚滲透性不如[[兩棲動物|兩棲動物]]這一點也使得其體内鹽分無法通過皮膚排出<ref name="Hazard">{{cite book | last = Hazard | first = Lisa C. | title = Sodium and Potassium Secretion by Iguana Salt Glands | work = Iguanas: Biology and Conservation | publisher = University of California Press | pages = 84–85 | year = 2004 | isbn = 978-0-520-23854-1 }}</ref>。

